1
00:00:06,868 --> 00:00:11,305
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

2
00:00:11,373 --> 00:00:14,900
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

3
00:00:14,976 --> 00:00:18,412
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

4
00:00:18,480 --> 00:00:22,075
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh! Just go my way</i>

5
00:00:22,150 --> 00:00:25,415
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

6
00:00:25,487 --> 00:00:27,421
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>

7
00:00:29,224 --> 00:00:32,159
<i>Down a difficult road</i>
<i>filled with endless struggles</i>

8
00:00:32,227 --> 00:00:36,027
<i>Where do you think you are going</i>
<i>following someone else's map?</i>

9
00:00:36,431 --> 00:00:43,269
<i>An insightful crow comes along</i>
<i>to tear up the map</i>

10
00:00:43,505 --> 00:00:50,570
<i>Now open your eyes and</i>
<i>take a look at the truth (Yeah!)</i>

11
00:00:50,879 --> 00:00:57,011
<i>There's nothing to lose,</i>
<i>so let's GO!!!</i>

12
00:00:57,152 --> 00:01:01,418
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

13
00:01:01,490 --> 00:01:05,085
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

14
00:01:05,160 --> 00:01:08,493
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

15
00:01:08,563 --> 00:01:12,192
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh!</i>
<i>Just go my way</i>

16
00:01:12,267 --> 00:01:15,862
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

17
00:01:15,937 --> 00:01:19,429
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best!</i>

18
00:01:19,508 --> 00:01:23,103
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

19
00:01:23,178 --> 00:01:27,274
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best! BANG!</i>

20
00:01:53,686 --> 00:01:55,415
Huh? Uh... excuse me...

21
00:02:15,775 --> 00:02:21,611
<i>Return of the Morning Mist</i>

22
00:02:34,894 --> 00:02:37,863
My mother and my father...
They didn't have to die.

23
00:02:39,231 --> 00:02:42,723
Because I didn't have strength,
the whole clan was destroyed.

24
00:02:44,403 --> 00:02:45,734
Everyone was killed...

25
00:02:57,216 --> 00:02:58,148
Darn it...

26
00:03:04,724 --> 00:03:06,021
Morning training is over!

27
00:03:18,237 --> 00:03:19,397
Once I've eaten breakfast

28
00:03:19,472 --> 00:03:21,667
I'll get back to rigorous training!

29
00:03:32,118 --> 00:03:33,278
<i>Old man...</i>

30
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:35,412
<i>Konohamaru...</i>

31
00:03:38,090 --> 00:03:39,489
Yo! Konohomaru.

32
00:03:44,497 --> 00:03:45,896
Naruto.

33
00:03:47,266 --> 00:03:49,598
Have you already resumed studies
at the academy?

34
00:03:49,702 --> 00:03:51,932
N-No, not yet.

35
00:03:52,104 --> 00:03:55,130
The school buildings are damaged,
so we're all repairing them.

36
00:03:55,474 --> 00:03:56,600
Is that so?

37
00:03:59,445 --> 00:04:02,107
How about you, Naruto?
You're already training?

38
00:04:02,948 --> 00:04:03,972
Sort of.

39
00:04:09,121 --> 00:04:11,385
Wh-What?

40
00:04:11,791 --> 00:04:12,985
What is it?

41
00:04:13,058 --> 00:04:14,650
N-No, it's nothing...

42
00:04:17,296 --> 00:04:18,558
- Hey um...!
- Hey um...!

43
00:04:19,198 --> 00:04:21,496
So what is it...?

44
00:04:22,434 --> 00:04:24,698
You too, Naruto, what is it?

45
00:04:25,571 --> 00:04:27,471
Nothing... really...

46
00:04:30,709 --> 00:04:32,176
I don't feel Ionely.

47
00:04:32,244 --> 00:04:32,903
Huh?

48
00:04:33,846 --> 00:04:36,178
There's no time to be feeling Ionely.

49
00:04:36,549 --> 00:04:41,577
Everyone is working really hard
to rebuild the village right now.

50
00:04:43,622 --> 00:04:44,611
Konohamaru...

51
00:04:45,524 --> 00:04:48,584
Right now, I must work for
the village even just a little bit.

52
00:04:49,328 --> 00:04:52,729
So Naruto, you work hard
at your training too.

53
00:04:53,265 --> 00:04:56,359
If you don't,
I'll become Hokage before you.

54
00:04:56,535 --> 00:05:00,471
Fool, I will absolutely become Hokage

55
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:04,105
Besides... you have to graduate
from the Academy first.

56
00:05:05,978 --> 00:05:07,036
Oh, that's right...

57
00:05:09,415 --> 00:05:10,848
Oh, here it is.

58
00:05:10,916 --> 00:05:12,247
Here, it's for you.

59
00:05:12,518 --> 00:05:13,849
A free ramen ticket from Ichiraku...

60
00:05:14,753 --> 00:05:15,879
Is it okay?

61
00:05:16,155 --> 00:05:20,353
I already have one,
so I'm giving one to you.

62
00:05:20,659 --> 00:05:22,217
Thank you, Naruto.

63
00:05:22,494 --> 00:05:24,189
Oh! Konohamaru.

64
00:05:24,263 --> 00:05:25,059
Good morning.

65
00:05:25,965 --> 00:05:26,989
I'm going to go.

66
00:05:28,500 --> 00:05:29,694
We'll work hard again today.

67
00:05:29,835 --> 00:05:30,529
- Yep!
- Yep!

68
00:05:31,503 --> 00:05:33,801
Today we're fixing the blackboards.

69
00:05:34,406 --> 00:05:35,771
I brought paint.

70
00:05:36,008 --> 00:05:41,241
Well! Once I've eaten ramen at Ichiraku,
I'll continue training.

71
00:05:55,327 --> 00:05:56,021
This is it.

72
00:05:58,797 --> 00:05:59,923
Th-This is...

73
00:06:04,803 --> 00:06:06,293
Alot of time has passed since the death.

74
00:06:07,106 --> 00:06:10,007
It's probably before
the Chunin Exam began.

75
00:06:10,809 --> 00:06:13,573
I see, so that's it...

76
00:06:15,781 --> 00:06:18,306
That Orochimaru!

77
00:06:22,288 --> 00:06:24,085
After the murder of Lord Kazekage,

78
00:06:24,590 --> 00:06:28,651
Orochimaru... or someone
like Kabuto played Kazekage...

79
00:06:29,962 --> 00:06:31,361
How thoughtless we were...

80
00:06:38,370 --> 00:06:40,395
That darn Sarutobi...

81
00:06:41,740 --> 00:06:43,867
Well, it's not that easy.

82
00:06:44,743 --> 00:06:47,405
The one who was your opponent
was the renowned Hokage

83
00:06:47,479 --> 00:06:50,004
deemed to be strongest of
all five great nations.

84
00:06:51,317 --> 00:06:55,344
However... you've done well.
Two out of the five Kages...

85
00:06:55,421 --> 00:06:56,854
Stop...

86
00:06:57,990 --> 00:07:01,585
Stop giving me words of sympathy.

87
00:07:03,128 --> 00:07:04,390
I will kill you!

88
00:07:08,267 --> 00:07:11,259
Of course, I didn't mean to...

89
00:07:11,770 --> 00:07:13,897
It's true that we didn't succeed
in bringing the village down...

90
00:07:16,241 --> 00:07:20,507
On the other hand, another objective
of this plan, Sasuke Uchiha...

91
00:07:21,313 --> 00:07:24,510
Your leash is now on him.

92
00:07:27,286 --> 00:07:32,417
In exchange for these arms
and all of my Jutsu...

93
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:38,560
If we could have gotten our hands
on that Itachi Uchiha from the beginning,

94
00:07:38,630 --> 00:07:40,461
it wouldn't have been a problem.

95
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:44,727
However that's a dream that
can no longer come true.

96
00:07:45,337 --> 00:07:48,829
He is stronger than I am.

97
00:07:53,512 --> 00:07:59,212
That is why... I pulled myself out
from that organization...

98
00:08:11,730 --> 00:08:12,594
Kakashi, huh?

99
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:15,897
What does he want?

100
00:08:17,636 --> 00:08:19,866
Breakfast, breakfast!

101
00:08:20,005 --> 00:08:22,599
Wait for me, my ramen.

102
00:08:29,348 --> 00:08:30,781
Do you already know
his whereabouts?

103
00:08:31,817 --> 00:08:32,613
Yes.

104
00:08:34,453 --> 00:08:36,250
In that case, it will be easy...

105
00:08:37,222 --> 00:08:37,984
Let's go.

106
00:08:41,093 --> 00:08:42,788
Here it comes, here it comes.

107
00:08:43,495 --> 00:08:45,861
Oh goodie, it's just like I thought.

108
00:08:46,365 --> 00:08:52,065
Hidden Leaf Village...
has a high average score.

109
00:08:52,171 --> 00:08:55,231
You're still doing such
a ridiculous thing?

110
00:08:55,874 --> 00:08:58,172
Well yes, this is my research.

111
00:08:59,845 --> 00:09:02,473
Old Man Homura and Koharu Sensei, huh?

112
00:09:03,982 --> 00:09:07,042
I wonder what you advisers
want from me.

113
00:09:07,619 --> 00:09:09,416
Surely, you know...

114
00:09:09,721 --> 00:09:12,451
without our telling you, don't you?

115
00:09:20,999 --> 00:09:23,467
You don't have to make
such scary faces.

116
00:09:23,535 --> 00:09:26,766
I heard that the talks with Sand Village
have been settled without problems.

117
00:09:27,739 --> 00:09:29,229
The Hidden Village in the Sand
announced that

118
00:09:29,308 --> 00:09:32,402
everything was Orochimaru's handiwork.

119
00:09:33,011 --> 00:09:38,244
In addition, at the moment of their
complete surrender to us, the Leaf Village,

120
00:09:38,317 --> 00:09:41,218
that wasn't a very important issue
any more.

121
00:09:41,854 --> 00:09:45,585
Leaf Village has no choice but
to accept their surrender and proposition

122
00:09:45,657 --> 00:09:47,318
in order to restore national power.

123
00:09:48,093 --> 00:09:53,690
However, the current strength of
Leaf Village has dropped drastically.

124
00:09:54,500 --> 00:09:55,626
Under these conditions,

125
00:09:55,701 --> 00:10:00,570
our top priority must be to prepare
for any unpredicted crisis.

126
00:10:01,073 --> 00:10:03,598
We don't know when any of
the neighboring nations

127
00:10:03,675 --> 00:10:05,609
will come out in a bold move.

128
00:10:06,044 --> 00:10:09,036
Therefore, we've decided that until
the village gets its strength back,

129
00:10:09,114 --> 00:10:12,208
we should assemble the top few men
from each troop,

130
00:10:12,284 --> 00:10:16,744
and form an emergency
executive committee to handle this.

131
00:10:18,190 --> 00:10:19,987
But first...

132
00:10:23,529 --> 00:10:26,259
we need a strong, trustworthy leader.

133
00:10:27,199 --> 00:10:30,862
You can find the seeds of trouble
rolling around everywhere these days.

134
00:10:31,370 --> 00:10:33,031
It's not just Orochimaru.

135
00:10:33,305 --> 00:10:37,366
You didn't have to go through
the trouble of informing me that.

136
00:10:38,443 --> 00:10:40,843
Well... I'll continue gathering materials.

137
00:10:40,913 --> 00:10:43,507
I'm going to tell you the basic plan.

138
00:10:44,016 --> 00:10:47,247
We need the Fifth Hokage right away.

139
00:10:47,386 --> 00:10:52,449
And yesterday at an emergency meeting
with the feudal lord of the Land of Fire,

140
00:10:52,791 --> 00:10:54,656
we decided
it would be you, Jiraiya.

141
00:10:57,129 --> 00:11:00,326
I'm sorry, it's not my nature.

142
00:11:00,799 --> 00:11:02,130
It has been decided.

143
00:11:02,367 --> 00:11:06,064
Besides, if a Shinobi like you,
renowned as a Sannin, is not...

144
00:11:06,138 --> 00:11:07,230
then who is?

145
00:11:09,575 --> 00:11:12,043
If you want a Sannin,
there is one more left...

146
00:11:15,113 --> 00:11:16,740
That Tsunade.

147
00:11:20,052 --> 00:11:23,180
Certainly that child probably
has that capability, but...

148
00:11:23,956 --> 00:11:26,550
However, no one knows where she is.

149
00:11:27,059 --> 00:11:30,495
I'll find and bring her back.
If I do that there's no problem, right?

150
00:11:31,263 --> 00:11:32,195
But...

151
00:11:33,298 --> 00:11:37,792
A wise one like Tsunade is meant to
be Hokage more than I, with no motivation.

152
00:11:40,539 --> 00:11:41,733
What do you want to do?

153
00:11:44,376 --> 00:11:46,936
All right.
We'll give it urgent consideration.

154
00:11:47,379 --> 00:11:50,143
However, we'll have three members
from Anbu Black Ops to accompany you

155
00:11:50,215 --> 00:11:51,978
as the search unit for Tsunade.

156
00:11:52,417 --> 00:11:57,753
Don't worry, I won't escape from this.
The guards are not necessary.

157
00:11:59,124 --> 00:12:00,182
However...

158
00:12:02,294 --> 00:12:05,422
There is one guy that I want
to take with me on my trip.

159
00:12:06,365 --> 00:12:09,357
I've found an interesting egg...

160
00:12:10,771 --> 00:12:14,138
What? That is absolutely strange.

161
00:12:14,307 --> 00:12:17,037
Sorry, but if you don't have a ticket,
there's no ramen.

162
00:12:17,277 --> 00:12:20,678
No, wait a minute!
I absolutely had one more.

163
00:12:21,281 --> 00:12:22,213
Huh?

164
00:12:22,282 --> 00:12:24,944
The one that I gave Konohamaru,
was it the last?

165
00:12:27,154 --> 00:12:28,348
Welcome!

166
00:12:32,993 --> 00:12:35,587
Hey, my ramen!

167
00:12:38,198 --> 00:12:39,563
"Racy Violence"

168
00:12:41,635 --> 00:12:43,068
Yo, you two!

169
00:12:44,538 --> 00:12:46,403
You seem to be getting along well.

170
00:12:46,973 --> 00:12:50,636
Fool, Anko asked me to
buy rice dumplings. That's all.

171
00:12:50,977 --> 00:12:53,605
What are <i>you</i> doing here?

172
00:12:53,980 --> 00:12:59,247
While I'm here to buy offerings,
I've made plans to meet here...

173
00:13:00,353 --> 00:13:01,718
with Sasuke.

174
00:13:03,356 --> 00:13:06,484
Huh, it's rare that you wait for people.

175
00:13:07,594 --> 00:13:09,221
Is the offering to Obito?

176
00:13:09,663 --> 00:13:10,527
Obito?

177
00:13:11,398 --> 00:13:13,229
Well... that's about right.

178
00:13:20,707 --> 00:13:24,074
Kakashi, it's strange for
you to be here first.

179
00:13:24,578 --> 00:13:26,944
Well... once in a while.

180
00:13:34,888 --> 00:13:37,550
I don't do <i>natto</i> (fermented beans)
And sweet things.

181
00:13:38,091 --> 00:13:39,683
Oh... Is that so?

182
00:13:50,137 --> 00:13:51,570
What?!

183
00:13:51,638 --> 00:13:54,869
This is absolutely positively strange!

184
00:14:10,457 --> 00:14:14,917
You guys aren't from the village...
Why in the world did you come?

185
00:14:15,495 --> 00:14:18,464
I haven't seen you for
a while Asuma, Kurenai.

186
00:14:18,865 --> 00:14:23,768
If you know about us,
are you former Leaf Shinobi?

187
00:14:32,479 --> 00:14:33,377
- Huh?!
- Huh?!

188
00:14:34,047 --> 00:14:35,446
Y-You are?!

189
00:14:46,593 --> 00:14:48,754
Humph, without a doubt...

190
00:14:50,730 --> 00:14:51,924
Uchiha...

191
00:14:53,533 --> 00:14:54,295
Itachi.

192
00:14:57,737 --> 00:14:59,898
You are acquaintances of Itachi?

193
00:15:01,641 --> 00:15:02,608
If so...

194
00:15:03,476 --> 00:15:05,910
I'll introduce myself as well.

195
00:15:08,949 --> 00:15:10,780
I'm Kisame Hoshigaki.

196
00:15:11,284 --> 00:15:13,252
Hereafter, I hope to be familiar with you.

197
00:15:15,422 --> 00:15:20,223
Never mind later,
I'm going to beat you now!

198
00:15:20,694 --> 00:15:21,888
Itachi...

199
00:15:22,529 --> 00:15:25,965
It seems you're pretty unpopular
in the village too.

200
00:15:26,533 --> 00:15:27,795
I know you, too.

201
00:15:28,401 --> 00:15:29,868
Kisame Hoshigake,

202
00:15:29,936 --> 00:15:31,904
originally a Shinobi
of Hidden Village in the Mist.

203
00:15:32,072 --> 00:15:35,439
Suspected of national covert activities
and of killing a feudal lord,

204
00:15:35,508 --> 00:15:39,103
a Rogue Ninja from Land of Water,
on the wanted list in all nations.

205
00:15:40,013 --> 00:15:44,677
You're a major S rank criminal
listed in the Bingo Book.

206
00:15:47,520 --> 00:15:52,685
Itachi, you have some nerve
coming back to this village

207
00:15:52,993 --> 00:15:54,585
after causing that awful incident.

208
00:15:55,528 --> 00:15:56,893
Asuma... Kurenai...

209
00:15:57,931 --> 00:15:59,660
Don't interfere with me.

210
00:16:01,034 --> 00:16:03,059
I don't intend to kill you.

211
00:16:03,803 --> 00:16:07,864
That's not a line for you,
who killed your comrades.

212
00:16:08,909 --> 00:16:10,604
I know there's no way
you'd come here

213
00:16:10,777 --> 00:16:15,111
without any clear purpose
in those suspicious appearance.

214
00:16:16,549 --> 00:16:17,811
What are you after?

215
00:16:23,323 --> 00:16:27,054
This guy is pretty annoying.
Should we kill him?

216
00:16:27,727 --> 00:16:30,252
It doesn't look like we are able
to leave the village so smoothly...

217
00:16:31,498 --> 00:16:35,491
But don't overdo it,
your techniques tend to stand out.

218
00:16:36,803 --> 00:16:38,168
They're done for then.

219
00:17:20,447 --> 00:17:21,243
<i>This is...</i>

220
00:17:22,983 --> 00:17:24,007
<i>Genjutsu.</i>

221
00:17:32,692 --> 00:17:36,594
<i>Pressing down with the tip of his sword...</i>
<i>What strength.</i>

222
00:17:39,599 --> 00:17:41,931
<i>My large sword, Shark Skin...</i>

223
00:17:51,044 --> 00:17:53,979
<i>doesn't cut, but lops it off!</i>

224
00:18:01,154 --> 00:18:02,951
Kurenai... You're late.

225
00:18:28,281 --> 00:18:29,305
With this...

226
00:18:30,650 --> 00:18:31,548
it's over!

227
00:18:38,291 --> 00:18:41,089
Genjutsu of that level doesn't work on me.

228
00:18:41,795 --> 00:18:44,320
<i>This is...Genjutsu Reversal?</i>

229
00:19:05,752 --> 00:19:06,616
Kurenai!

230
00:19:06,686 --> 00:19:09,086
There's no time to look away.

231
00:19:10,223 --> 00:19:12,691
That's what's expected from you, Kurenai.

232
00:19:12,759 --> 00:19:13,453
But...

233
00:19:15,862 --> 00:19:18,296
"But this is as far as it goes...

234
00:19:19,466 --> 00:19:20,524
for you.

235
00:19:28,575 --> 00:19:29,303
What?!

236
00:19:37,250 --> 00:19:38,182
<i>Water Style!</i>

237
00:19:43,656 --> 00:19:45,180
- <i>Water Shark Bomb Jutsu!</i>
- <i>Water Shark Bomb Jutsu!</i>

238
00:19:50,296 --> 00:19:51,923
The same Jutsu as me?!

239
00:19:52,532 --> 00:19:55,057
Why have you shown up too?

240
00:19:55,668 --> 00:19:59,434
Well... I asked you to take care
of them earlier.

241
00:20:00,206 --> 00:20:02,436
But I kinda felt uneasy, you know.

242
00:20:03,543 --> 00:20:04,532
Shadow clones.

243
00:20:06,112 --> 00:20:07,545
Kakashi...

244
00:20:07,947 --> 00:20:08,971
Hatake.

245
00:20:13,019 --> 00:20:14,577
Cripes... So much fuss for nothing.

246
00:20:16,089 --> 00:20:17,954
I...

247
00:20:18,291 --> 00:20:20,156
I put it under my headband

248
00:20:20,226 --> 00:20:25,163
in order not to drop the important ticket
during morning training.

249
00:20:27,867 --> 00:20:31,894
Okay, that's fine...
Eat well and do your best.

250
00:20:32,071 --> 00:20:32,833
Hmm?

251
00:20:33,773 --> 00:20:36,207
You're going to do it again
after this, right? Training?

252
00:20:40,046 --> 00:20:42,378
Of course! I'm full of motivation.

253
00:20:42,515 --> 00:20:43,777
Good! Here you go.

254
00:20:47,353 --> 00:20:49,844
Another serving for free! Go for it!

255
00:20:50,190 --> 00:20:51,748
Thank you, sir!

256
00:20:54,060 --> 00:20:55,152
Welcome.

257
00:20:55,228 --> 00:20:57,389
Just like I heard...
I had to come and see it.

258
00:20:58,331 --> 00:21:01,664
It seems that you really
are just eating ramen.

259
00:21:02,368 --> 00:21:04,336
Oh, Pervy Sage!

260
00:21:09,175 --> 00:21:13,111
<i>A cycle of hardship, right?</i>

261
00:21:14,113 --> 00:21:18,072
<i>Inside, we were crying, right?</i>

262
00:21:19,385 --> 00:21:27,485
<i>But the one thing we won't give up</i>
<i>is the dream we've chosen, right?</i>

263
00:21:28,328 --> 00:21:30,421
<i>It's a secondary role,</i>

264
00:21:33,199 --> 00:21:36,225
<i>a role in the shadows</i>

265
00:21:36,669 --> 00:21:41,606
<i>But in reaching for that dream,</i>

266
00:21:41,741 --> 00:21:47,202
<i>let us stay centered,</i>
<i>let us stay true</i>

267
00:21:47,480 --> 00:21:52,383
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we hung on without giving up</i>

268
00:21:52,452 --> 00:21:57,355
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we kept coming back up</i>

269
00:21:57,423 --> 00:22:06,593
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we believed and dreamed</i>

270
00:22:07,033 --> 00:22:12,164
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we've seen fools</i>

271
00:22:12,238 --> 00:22:17,835
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we've stood in the shadows of others</i>

272
00:22:19,479 --> 00:22:29,616
<i>Now, it's our turn...</i>
<i>Let us bask in our dreams</i>

273
00:22:37,263 --> 00:22:38,457
Uchiha Itachi...

274
00:22:39,332 --> 00:22:41,425
who became a leader of
Anbu Black Ops at the age of thirteen

275
00:22:41,968 --> 00:22:45,062
and who destroyed
the Uchiha clan single-handedly.

276
00:22:46,372 --> 00:22:49,364
I don't know why he has
suddenly appeared after all this time...

277
00:22:49,842 --> 00:22:53,437
But I don't think we will
allow him to leave so easily.

278
00:22:54,947 --> 00:22:58,383
What is your purpose?!

279
00:23:00,186 --> 00:23:02,916
Next time: "Sharingan vs. Sharingan!"
